#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Appointments App</b>: Offer seamless online booking for consultations and "
"sessions, allowing clients to schedule\n"
"                time with you 24/7."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application Rendez-vous</b> : offrez une réservation en ligne fluide pour "
"les consultations et les séances, permettant aux clients de planifier du "
"temps avec vous 24h/24 et 7j/7."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Calendar App</b>: Manage your daily schedule efficiently, avoiding double "
"bookings and ensuring you have adequate\n"
"                preparation time between clients."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application Calendrier</b> : gérez efficacement votre planning quotidien, "
"évitez les doubles réservations et assurez-vous de disposer de suffisamment "
"de temps de préparation entre les clients."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Contacts App</b>: Maintain a clean and organized directory of all your "
"clients, suppliers, and professional\n"
"                partners."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application Contacts</b> : maintenez un répertoire clair et organisé de "
"tous vos clients, fournisseurs et partenaires professionnels."

#. module: wellness_practitioner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:wellness_practitioner.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b>Invoicing App</b>: Simplify your finances by generating professional "
"invoices for sessions and packages, ensuring\n"
"                you get paid on time."
msgstr ""
"<b>Application Facturation</b> : simplifiez vos finances en générant des "
"factures professionnelles pour les séances et les forfaits, afin d’être payé "
"à temps."

